tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE green_transport_incentives (
  incentive_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  incentive_name VARCHAR(255),
  provider_name VARCHAR(255),
  description TEXT,
  start_date DATE,
  end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE green_transportation_incentives (
    incentive_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    incentive_name VARCHAR(255),
    organization_name VARCHAR(255),
    incentive_amount DECIMAL,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE government_subsidies (
    subsidy_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    subsidy_program VARCHAR(255),
    description TEXT,
    government_agency VARCHAR(255),
    eligibility_criteria TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE green_transportation_incentives (
    incentive_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    incentive_name VARCHAR(100),
    organization_name VARCHAR(100),
    amount DECIMAL(10,2),
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE government_incentives (
    government_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    government_name VARCHAR(100),
    region VARCHAR(50),
    budget DECIMAL(15,2),
    contact_person VARCHAR(100),
    contact_email VARCHAR(100)
);

CREATE TABLE organization_incentives (
    org_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    org_name VARCHAR(100),
    type VARCHAR(50),
    description TEXT,
    contact_person VARCHAR(100),
    contact_email VARCHAR(100)
);

CREATE TABLE incentives (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  name VARCHAR(50),
  description TEXT,
  amount DECIMAL(10,2),
  start_date DATE,
  end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE locations (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  location_name VARCHAR(100),
  address TEXT,
  city VARCHAR(50),
  country VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE participants (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  name VARCHAR(50),
  email VARCHAR(100),
  organization_id INT,
  FOREIGN KEY (organization_id) REFERENCES organizations(id)
);

CREATE TABLE green_transportation_incentives (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(50),
    description TEXT,
    amount DECIMAL(10, 2),
    organization VARCHAR(100)
);

CREATE TABLE government_subsidies (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    program_name VARCHAR(50),
    agency VARCHAR(100),
    eligibility_criteria TEXT,
    amount DECIMAL(10, 2)
);

CREATE TABLE incentives_eligibility (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    incentive_id INT,
    eligible_for VARCHAR(100),
    eligibility_criteria TEXT,
    FOREIGN KEY (incentive_id) REFERENCES green_transportation_incentives(id)
);

CREATE TABLE subsidy_distribution (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    subsidy_id INT,
    organization VARCHAR(100),
    amount_allocated DECIMAL(10, 2),
    FOREIGN KEY (subsidy_id) REFERENCES government_subsidies(id)
);

CREATE TABLE organization (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(100),
    type VARCHAR(50),
    headquarters_location VARCHAR(200),
    website VARCHAR(200)
);
